						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1494 (1572 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers gift of lands and gold towards offerings to god by <hi rend="italic">Rāyasam</hi> <hi rend="bold">Tirumalaiyyan, son of Timmappar of Anumaṉkuṟichchi.</hi> The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1494, Āṅgira, Simha śu. 2, •••• , Uttira correspond to 1572 A.D. August 10, (Sunday), ·79.</hi></p>						

